description: I’m in shock. 2 days ago one of my Patrons sent me a link to a YouTube video & said “you’re welcome”.... that link took me to a video from almost 2 years ago that had less than 2,000 views. It hit home with me & I knew I had to share it. After I did that, people were demanding to find out who this was & someone was able to find his Twitter handle for me. And when I found his Twitter, he had his messages turned off so I had to mention him in a comment to try to get his attention (this was one post after the post that Q mentioned me in) - and he messaged me back! The first thing he asked me was how we stand up & save America & I said something along the lines of doing it TOGETHER. And sure enough @fleccas saw the video & shared it - which was then seen by @danscavino who shared it on Twitter. And now @semore_views has gone viral. And nobody deserves it more than him! I just wanted to share this story with you guys because it is the PERFECT example of WWG1WGA. Nobody is more significant than anybody else in this movement. We all have a voice to be heard & are all in this together for a common cause - TO DESTROY EVIL. Thank you God for giving my brother @semore_views a platform to be heard from. He’s going to do some BIG things for this nation - as well as the rest of the world. 🙏🏻🌎💯 #WWG1WGA #DarkToLight #TheGreatAwakening #JesusIsCool #GodWins #PatriotsAreInControl #InItTogether #TrustThePlan #PanicInDC #Qanon #TheStormIsUponUs #StrongerTogether #JusticeIsComing #NothingCanStopWhatsComing
